hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 擦边角动量 $L_{0}$ 由 $r=R$ 处的转折点条件定义：
$$E=\frac{\alpha}{R}+\frac{L_{0}^{2}\hbar^{2}}{2\mu R^{2}}\,. $$
解出 $L_{0}^{2}$ 可得
$$L_{0}^{2}
= \frac{2\mu R^{2}}{\hbar^{2}}\Bigl(E-\frac{\alpha}{R}\Bigr)
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
L_{0}
= \frac{R}{\hbar}\sqrt{2\mu\Bigl(E-\frac{\alpha}{R}\Bigr)}\,. $$

2. $L$ 的微小变化通过以下方式改变最近距离 $r_{\min}$：
$$0
= \frac{d}{dL}\Bigl[\alpha/r_{\min}+L^{2}\hbar^{2}/(2\mu r_{\min}^{2})-E\Bigr]
=\Bigl(-\frac{\alpha}{r^{2}}-\frac{L^{2}\hbar^{2}}{\mu r^{3}}\Bigr)\frac{dr}{dL}
+\frac{L\hbar^{2}}{\mu r^{2}}\,. $$
因此
$$\frac{dr}{dL}
=\frac{\dfrac{L\hbar^{2}}{\mu r^{2}}}
{\dfrac{\alpha}{r^{2}}+\dfrac{L^{2}\hbar^{2}}{\mu r^{3}}}
=\frac{L\hbar^{2}\,r}{\mu\bigl(\alpha\,r+L^{2}\hbar^{2}/\mu\bigr)}\,. $$

3. 在擦边点 $r=R$, $L=L_{0}$ 处求值： 
$$\alpha R+ \frac{L_{0}^{2}\hbar^{2}}{\mu}
=\alpha R+2R^{2}\Bigl(E-\frac{\alpha}{R}\Bigr)
=R(2RE-\alpha)\,. $$
于是
$$\left.\frac{dr}{dL}\right|_{L_{0}}
=\frac{L_{0}\hbar^{2}}{\mu\,(2RE-\alpha)}\,. $$

4. 宽度 $\Delta L$ 通过要求 $\delta r\sim\delta_{R}$ 来设定：
$$\Delta L\approx\frac{\delta_{R}}{\bigl|dr/dL\bigr|}
=\delta_{R}\,\frac{\mu\,(2RE-\alpha)}{L_{0}\hbar^{2}}\,. $$

5. 无量纲乘积为
$$P=L_{0}\,\Delta L
=\frac{\mu\,(2RE-\alpha)\,\delta_{R}}{\hbar^{2}}\,. $$
